posts.text:

Borsa, dolar ve euroda son durum! 
Merkez Bankası'nın TL likidetisini azaltırken, bankaların döviz kullanımını artıracak önlemleri ve ABD vize adımı ile düşen dolar ve euro yeni günde yatay seyrederken, Borsa, dünkü rekor kapanışın ardından yeni güne de yükselerek başladı. editör1 07 Kasım 2017 Salı 12:22 
Yeni haftaya 3.88 liranın üzerinde başlayan dolar , Merkez Bankası'nın döviz likidetisine ilişkin düzünlemeler ile, piyasadan 5.3 milyar lira çekerken, yaklaşık 1.4 milyar dolar döviz bankaların kullanımına bırakması üzerine dün 3.84 - 3.85 lira, euro da 4.45 - 4.46 lira aralığına çekildi. ABD ve Avrupa para birimleri yeni güne de bu düzeylerde başladıktan sonra dolar 3.45 liranın, euro da 4.46 liranın üzerine çıktı. 
Merkez Bankası'ndan dün yapılan açaklamada, "Son dönemde piyasalarda ekonomik temellerle uyumlu olmayan sağlıksız fiyat oluşumları gözlenmektedir. Bu durum dikkate alınarak, fiyat istikrarına ve finansal istikrara destek sağlanması maksadıyla rezerv opsiyonu mekanizması kapsamında döviz imkânına ilişkin üst sınır ile dilim aralıklarında değişiklik yapılmıştır" denildi. 
Buna göre Merkez Bankası rezerv opsiyonu mekanizması kapsamında döviz imkân oranı üst sınırını yüzde 60'tan yüzde 55'e düşürürken, tüm dilim aralıkları da 5'er puan aşağı çekti. 
Borsa İstanbul Endeksi, yüzde 2.58 artışla 114 bin 165 puan ile yeni rekor düzeyden kapattığı dünkü işlemlerin ardından, yeni günde de yüzde 0.24 artışla 114 bin 442 puan ile açıldı. 
Buna karşılık gösterge iki yıllık tahvilin bileşik faizi dün de yükselmeye devam etti. Geçen haftayı yüzde yüzde 13.29'dan kapatan faiz, dünkü kapanışta yüzde 13.50'ye kadar tırmanırken, yeni güne yüzde 13.36 dolayında başladıktan sonra yeniden yüzde 13.45'e çıktı. 
BIST'de yeni zirveye vize.... 
İş Yatırım'ın, "BIST'de yeni zirveye vize...." başlıklı günlük piyasa bülteninde, "Dün öğleden sonra ABD’nin Türkiye’den vize başvurularını sınırlı olarak kabul edeceğini açıklamasının ardından BIST 100 Endeksi 114 bin 165 ile yeni bir lira bazında kapanış zirvesi yaptı" denildi ve şu değerlendirme yapıldı: 
"Akşam saatlerinde ABD Büyükelçiliği, Türk Hükümetinin bundan sonra yerel konsolosluk çalışanları ile ilgili gözaltına alma ya da tutuklama niyetine ilişkin ABD hükümetine bilgi vermeyi taahhüt ettiğini açıkladı. 
"Daha sonra Türkiye Washington Büyükelçiliği tarafından yapılan açıklamada Hükümetin bu konuda herhangi bir güvence vermesinin söz konusu olmadığı belirtildi. 
"Bundan sonra gözler Çarşamba günü saat 18:30 da yapılacak Başkan Yıldırım ile ABD Bşk. Yard. Pence arasındaki görüşme sonrası yapılacak açıklamalarda olacak. 
"İki ülke arasındaki ilişkileri ile ilgili yapılabilecek olumlu açıklamalar TL varlıkların performansını desteklemeye devam edebilir. 
"MSCI (Morgan Stanley Capital International) Türkiye endeksi dünkü çıkışın ardından vize krizi öncesine göre yüzde 3.8 getiri ile, MSCI GOÜ (gelişmekte olan ülkeler) endeksinin üzerinde bir getiriye ulaşmış durumda (yüzde 2.53). 
"Öte yandan liranın aynı dönemdeki performansına baktığımızda yüzde 5.8 lik kayıpla Brezilya’nın (yüzde -2.9) ardından en son sırada. 
"Dolayısıyla, ABD ziyareti ile ilgili gelebilecek olumlu haberler kurun 3.75 düzeyine kadar çekilmesini sağlayabilir." 
DHA

15 Temmuz darbe girişiminin komuta merkezi olan Akıncı Üssü'ndeki eylemlere ilişkin 486 sanık hakkında açılan davanın görülmesine devam ediliyor. Dava dosyasına giren güvenlik kamera görüntülerinde, pistin bombalanması sırasında lojman bölgesindeki markette alış veriş yapan asker yakınlarının yaşadığı panik görülüyor. editör1 07 Kasım 2017 Salı 12:26 
Ankara 4. Ağır Ceza Mahkemesinde görülen dava dosyasına, o gün kayıt yapan Akıncı Üssü'ndeki güvenlik kameralarının görüntüleri de girdi. Lojmanlar bölgesindeki marketin güvenlik kamerasına yansıyan görüntülerde, 16 Temmuz sabahı saat 10.00 sıralarında alışveriş yapan asker ve yakınları görülüyor. Alışveriş yapanların panik halinde bol miktarda ekmek ve su aldıkları görüntülere yansıyor. 
Bu sırada darbecilerin üsten kalkışını önlemek için, Eskişehir'den kalkan jetler pisti bombalıyor ve jet seslerinin ardından patlama sesi duyuluyor. Güvenlik taburundan oldukları tahmin edilen bazı askerler markette bulunanların yere yatmasını istiyor. Herkes korku ve panik halinde yere yatıyor. Daha sonra bir asker, "Pist bombalanıyor, bizim her şeyden haberimiz var. Panik yapmayın" diye sesleniyor. Askerler markette bulunanları güvenli bir şekilde dışarı çıkartıyor. Korku ve panik için kaçışan asker yakınlarından bazılarının tekrar markete girip hızla bir şeyler almaya çalıştıkları görüntülere yansıyor.

posts.author: Alexandros G. Sfakianakis,Anapafseos 5 Agios Nikolaos 72100 Crete Greece,00306932607174,00302841026182 (noreply@blogger.com)
posts.title: Flowable composites for restoration of non-carious cervical lesions: Results after five years
posts.text:
Publication date: Available online 6 November 2017
Source: Dental Materials
Author(s): Fabian Cieplik, Konstantin J. Scholz, Isabelle Tabenski, Sabine May, Karl-Anton Hiller, Gottfried Schmalz, Wolfgang Buchalla, Marianne Federlin
ObjectivesTo evaluate the clinical performance of two flowable composites for restoration of Class-V non-carious cervical lesions (NCCLs), one with novel (N'Durance ® Dimer Flow, Septodont; ND) and one with modified conventional matrix composition (Filtek™ Supreme XTE Flow, 3M-ESPE; FS). The null hypothesis was that both flowable composite materials perform equally regarding clinical quality and survival.Methods50 patients received one ND and one FS restoration of NCCLs in premolars using Clearfil Protect Bond (Kuraray) as an adhesive without additional selective enamel etching. Restorations were evaluated at baseline (BL), after 30 and 60 months employing selected original FDI criteria and refined FDI criteria by separate evaluation of enamel and dentine margins. Non-parametric statistical analyses and χ 2 tests were applied (α=0.05).Results38 patients with both restorations under risk were available for the 60-mo recall (recall rate: 76%). At 60-mo, 94.7% of ND and 84.2% of FS restorations were rated clinically acceptable. No significant differences for all selected FDI criteria were recorded between ND and FS at each examination time point except for the criteria surface lustre at 60-mo, where FS showed significantly better results. No significant differences over time could be detected for both materials. There was a trend for more deterioration along the enamel margins than along the dentine margins (criteria marginal staining and marginal adaptation).SignificanceWithin the limitations of the study, the null hypothesis that materials perform equally could not be rejected. Both flowable composites performed similarly regarding clinical performance.

posts.title: دراسة: متلازمة تكيسات المبيض تزيد خطر الاضطرابات النفسية لدى النساء
posts.text: مرأة و طفل دقت دراسة طبية ناقوس الخطر من التأثير السلبي لمتلازمة تكيسات المبيض فى زيادة مخاطر معاناة المرأة من اضطرابات نفسية، وأوضح باحثون في جامعة "كاردييف" فى مقاطعة ويلز ببريطانيا أن متلازمة تكيس المبايض حالة شائعة تؤثر على ما بين 5 - 10% من النساء على مستوى العالم، حيث يمكن أن يؤدى إلى ارتفاع مستويات هرمون الذكورة إلى ظهور مجموعة من الأعراض المؤلمة، بما في ذلك انخفاض الخصوبة، والفترات غير المنتظمة للدورة الشهرية، وزيادة نسبة الشعر في الوجه والجسم، فضلا عن حب الشباب. وكانت دراسات سابقة قد اقترحت وجود صلة بين تكيس المبيض وسوء الصحة العقلية لدى النساء، لكنها لم تأخذ في الاعتبار على نحو كاف العوامل الأخرى التي يمكن أن تؤثر على الصحة العقلية، بالإضافة إلى ذلك تم الإبلاغ عن مستويات مرتفعة من هرمون الذكورة (التستوستيرون) أثناء الحمل، وهو ما قد يزيد من خطر الاضطرابات العصبية التنموية، مثل اضطراب فرط الحركة ونقص الانتباه والتوحد لدى حديثى الولادة. وفي هذه الدراسة، قام باحثون في "معهد أبحاث الأعصاب والصحة العقلية" بجامعة "كارديف" بتحليل تاريخ الصحة النفسية بأثر رجعى لأكثر من 17 ألف امرأة، وتم تشخيص إصابتهم بمتلازمة تكيس المبيض، وشملت الدراسة المريضات اللاتى تم تشخيص إصابتهن بمتلازمة تكيس المبايض عبر تقييمات المتابعة الروتينية لمدة لا تقل عن 6 أشهر. وبالمقارنة مع النساء المتضررات، المتطابقة مع العمر ومؤشر كتلة الجسم، وجدت الدراسة أن مرضى متلازمة تكيس المبيض كانوا أكثر عرضة لتشخيص اضطرابات الصحة النفسية، بما فى ذلك الاكتئاب والقلق واضطراب ثنائي القطب، كما وجد أن الأطفال الذين يولدون لأمهات مصابات بمتلازمة تكيس المبايض أكثر عرضة للإصابة بفرط الحركة ونقص الانتباه واضطراب طيف التوحد. وأشارت النتائج المتوصل إليها إلى أنه ينبغي فحص النساء المصابات بمتلازمة تكيس المبايض من أجل اضطرابات الصحة النفسية، لضمان التشخيص والعلاج المبكرين وتحسين نوعية حياتهن فى نهاية المطاف. وقال الدكتور ألد ريس أستاذ الأمراض النفسية والعقلية في جامعة (كاردييف) "لقد قللنا فى السابق من تأثير مرض تكيس المبايض على الصحة العقلية، حيث تظهر نتائج أبحاثنا ضرورة فحص اضطرابات الصحة النفسية وينبغي النظر فيها أثناء التقييمات السريرية". ويأمل الدكتور ريس ومجموعته البحثية فى معرفة ما إذا كانت العوامل الوراثية التى تسهم فى خطر تكيس المبايض تسهم أيضا فى خطر الإصابة بالتوحد واضطرابات فرط الحركة ونقص الانتباه أم لا، مما يساعد على الكشف عن مسارات بيولوجية متورطة فى هذه الاضطرابات وتؤدى إلى علاجات جديدة.

posts.text:
משרד הבריאות מונע מעמותת הקנאביס הרפואי בישראל לסייע לחולים מעריב לפני יום מעיין הרוני
משרד הבריאות מונע מעמותת הקנאביס הרפואי בישראל לסייע לחולים שמבקשים לקבל רישיון לטיפול בקנאביס או לחדשו. זאת, בשל הנחיות חדשות, שמבטלות את האפשרות שניתנה לחולים רבים לחתום מרצונם על כתב ויתור סודיות רפואית ולאפשר לעמותה לשמש כבאת כוחם.
© סופק על ידי מעריב נציג העמותה ניר אלישע התקשר פעמיים בשבועיים האחרונים ליק"ר (יחידה לקנאביס רפואי במשרד הבריאות) כדי לבדוק היכן עומדות פניותיהם של עשרות חולים המבקשים רישיון, אולם הנציגה לא אפשרה זאת.
ההתנהלות שבה נציג העמותה מטפל בפניותיהם של עשרות מטופלים היא כמעט הכרחית - למעלה מ־40 אלף פניות מתקבלות ביק"ר ברבעון. זמן ההמתנה, בהתאם, עשוי להגיע עד ארבע שעות, שלאחריהן השיחה מתנתקת לעתים מעצמה.
הווידוא שהבקשות, שנשלחות בפקס בלבד, התקבלו, הוא הכרחי, וניתן לבצעו רק טלפונית. לעתים הבקשה לא מתקבלת והטיפול בה מוקפא ללא הודעה לחולה. זאת, כאשר רבים מאותם חולים נמצאים במצב סיעודי או באשפוז, שאינם מאפשרים להם לדאוג לעצמם. אמנם ההנחיות החדשות מאפשרות לבן משפחה לברר בנוגע לפניית החולה, אך לא ניתן להוכיח קרבה משפחתית בשיחה טלפונית, דבר שמשרד הבריאות בעצמו אינו מכחיש.
לדברי דורון בלזר, חולה סיעודי שסובל מתשע פריצות דיסק בגבו, "אם לא העזרה של העמותה הייתי מת בבית".
ממשרד הבריאות נמסר בתגובה: "בירור מידע רפואי עבור מטופל יכול להיעשות על ידי המטופל, רופאו או מיופה כוחו כדין. באם מוצג ייפוי כוח – הפרטים נמסרים למיופה הכוח".

posts.title: Foreigners visiting Royal Crematorium express their respect for the late King
posts.text:
Foreigners visiting Royal Crematorium express their respect for the late King national November 07, 2017 13:46 By Marisa Chimprabha, Mayuree Sukyingcharoenwong The Nation The Royal Crematorium of HM the late King Bhumibol Adulyadej has been open to the pubฌlic since Thursday with people flocking to have a firsthand experience to see the splendid Merumas and other items built by masters of arts across the country for the much-beloved late King. 
Among the visitors have been foreigners who braved the crowds to queue to visit the cremaฌtorium and surrounding pavilions. 
One of them was Jacques Moreau, an adviser to the Princess Galyani Vadhana Institute of Music, who said the ceremonies for the late HM King were the first time that he had had a chance to see a Royal funeral. 
It had made a great impression on him perฌsonally, he said. 
Moreau had seen video footage of the Royal funeral for HRH Princess Galyani Vadhana that was held in November 15, 2008 after she passed away in January the same year. 
Because of that, Moreau said he knew what was going on, “but this Royal Funeral for King Rama IX is tremendously unique. There is no need to compare it to the Princess’s funeral.” 
“What impressed me a lot was all the people everywhere and the devotion of the Thai peoฌple to their beloved monarch. It is something unique in the world,” he said. 
Moreau said he had learned about the King’s devotion to his people and his good work. “This ceremony showed what he did for his people. Now I have discovered the really deep devotion the Thai people have for the King. There are no more questions of politics, of if you are with the monarchy or not.” 
He said that he was at Sanam Luang when the Royal Cremation was held on October 26. 
“I watched the cremation from outside. When the cremation started, there was a huge silence. Nobody moved. It was very deep emotional experience.” 
Talking about the Royal Cremation buildings, he said it was clear that everybody had done their best work in the most perfect homage they could give to their beloved King. 
Moreau said that when one laid the flowers for the late King, it was not the flower that matฌtered, it was that you had done it as an expresฌsion of last respect. 
“It is not only the matter of having beautiful [crematorium] buildings for the King. Each one would give what he knows best to do for that event,” he said. 
Apparently referring to criticism by some western media that the Royal funeral was too expensive, Moreau said western people might think the cost was too high and it should be spent somewhere else. 
“But when you witness it, you understand that it is not a question of money as it is a quesฌtion of respect, and a question of saying goodฌbye to 70 years of reign of a King who is with his people and of his people,” he said. 
He described the experience of watching the funeral as “a very unusual experience for the 21 century”. 
Also visiting the Royal Crematorium was Allan Macister from Australia, who is frequent visitor to Thailand, having visited the Kingdom about 20 times. He said he had waited in the line about two hours before being able to enter the premises. “I chose to visit Thailand during the late King’s Royal Funeral to be part of history. I was here during Princess Galyani’s cremation in 2008, and I came here this time especially for the Royal Funeral of King Rama IX.” 
Macister said the late King had done a lot for his country. “It is amazing how the crematorium buildings were built,” he added. 
He said it was a shame that they would be removed, but he was glad that many items would be placed in museums for people to see. 
He also said he would return to the ceremonial grounds again, as a one-hour visit was not enough for him to see all of the pavilions. 
Minke Dokter, from Holland, who visited the grounds with her husband, said that she had not had long to wait at the screening point before coming in. She also praised officials for handling the crowds, saying the venue was very well organised. 
Dokter, who has lived near Pattaya for many years, said she had read about and watched the Royal Funeral coverage on BBC news and come to Bangkok to see the crematorium with her own eyes. 
“I know that the late King did a lot for the Thai people. The crematorium and buildings are nicely done and I think it is very impressive,” she said.

Τι ισχύει για το ηλεκτρονικό εισιτήριο των 1,40 ευρώ Διατίθεται από τα εκδοτικά μηχανήματα • 07/11/2017 
Στην κυκλοφορία βγήκε από χθες το απλό εισιτήριο των 1,40 ευρώ με συγκεκριμένη χρονική διάρκεια, ενώ ταυτόχρονα δόθηκε σιωπηρή παράταση για το χάρτινο εισιτήριο που επρόκειτο να καταργηθεί από χθες. 
Μέχρι χθες είχαν ήδη εκδοθεί 220.000 προσωποποιημένες κάρτες, σύμφωνα με τα στοιχεία του ΟΑΣΑ. 
Από χθες διατίθεται από τα εκδοτικά μηχανήματα το μεμονωμένο ηλεκτρονικό εισιτήριο αξίας 1,40 ευρώ και διάρκειας 90 λεπτών. Η προτροπή του ΟΑΣΑ είναι να μην πετιέται το μεμονωμένο εισιτήριο, καθώς παρέχεται η δυνατότητα επαναφόρτισής του, ενώ εξετάζεται η παροχή κινήτρων για την επαναφόρτιση του μεμονωμένου εισιτηρίου. 
Ο ΟΑΣΑ αναμένει τη γνωμάτευση της Αρχής Προστασίας Δεδομένων Προσωπικού Χαρακτήρα όσον αφορά τα πρόσθετα αιτήματα που έθεσε. Μεταξύ αυτών, η δυνατότητα έκδοσης προσωποποιημένων καρτών μέσω Διαδικτύου και η μαζική έκδοση καρτών.

posts.text:
图集详情: 
【环球网综合报道】据 英国 《每日邮报》11月6日报道，由于生活成本的上涨，房屋租金的飙升， 美国 西海岸流浪人口持续增加，成千上万无固定居所的市民在公园、桥下、公路边搭起了临时居所，居住阵仗让人瞠目结舌。 
在西雅图一个绿树成荫的富人居住区中心的公园内，堆积了大量的家用废品——床垫、帐篷、木质用具、藤椅，只能由拖拉机清理，旁边还有带着面具穿着靴子的清洁工从草丛中捡拾被丢弃的针头和废物。就在前一天，这个公园还是流浪者的临时非法居所，400多个这样的非法居所涌现在西雅图各个公园、桥下、公路旁边。而现在，这些无家可归的人被警察和社会工作者从这样的非法居所驱赶出去，不得不回到城市汹涌的人潮中，又成了居无定所的人。 
这种情况不仅发生在西雅图，一场前所未有的流浪危机正席卷美国整个西海岸。而这一切归根结底是西海岸地区成功发展带来的后果——住房成本飙升，房屋空置率上涨，经济迅速发展。整个西海岸地区所有的政府官员都正在寻找解决办法。西雅图市议员迈克•奥布莱恩（Mike O'Brien）说，“西雅图失业率为零，但努力工作却无固定住房的人成千上万。这些没有房屋的居民没有地方可住。每次我们新开辟一个临时居所，都会挤满人。” 
越来越多无家可归的人将赤贫推向了前所未有的境界，同时也压倒了各个城市和非营利性组织。大量流浪人员露宿街头，公众健康受到威胁，多个城市宣告处于紧急情况，拨出巨款寻求解决方案。致命性甲型肝炎已在多个城市爆发，加利福尼亚州已发布紧急预警，圣迭哥正用漂白剂清洗人行道以防止致命性甲型肝炎的爆发。 
无家可归在西雅图并不是一件新鲜事。但加利福尼亚、俄勒冈州、华盛顿州官员及为流浪者提供服务的工作人员和美联社初步对流浪者统计得到的数据都显示，这种流浪情况正变得越来越糟。由于房价高涨，无论是曾经遭遇困境还 是安 然度过困境的人现在都被迫住在大街上。 
美国加利福尼亚、俄勒冈州、华盛顿州今年早些时候发布的官方数据显示，三个州总共有16.8万流浪者。由于包括了天气因素和其他因素造成的人口流浪，今年的人数相比前两年增长了1.9万人。 
美国房地产信息公司Zillow和华盛顿大学共同进行的一项研究表明，房价上涨和流浪人数之间存在着密切的联系。例如，洛杉矶房屋租金每增加5%，流浪人口将增加2000人。在政府和非营利组织的努力下，流浪者逐渐有了固定居所，因此全美范围内的流浪人口已经有下降趋势。西雅图政府已经开设了“低保障”庇护所，为流浪者提供床铺，但全市所供给的床铺数量较少，呈现供不应求的态势。（实习编译：王斐 审稿：朱盈库） 本网登载图片出于更直观传递信息之目的，并不代表本网赞同其观点和对其真实性负责，谢绝转载。如该图片涉及任何第三方合法权利，请及时与lawyer@huanqiu.com联系。 本图集所有图片已播放完毕

Serdar Ortaç’tan evliliğiyle ilgili açıklama Müzik dünyasına sunduğu başarılı albümlerle fenomenleşen ve zirvedeki yerini her daim koruyan Serdar Ortaç, yeni albümü 'Cımbız' ve müzikten evliliğine kadar bilinmeyenleri anlattı. Serdar Ortaç’tan evliliğiyle ilgili açıklama 
Müzik dünyasına sunduğu başarılı albümlerle fenomenleşen ve zirvedeki yerini her daim koruyan Serdar Ortaç, yeni albümü 'Cımbız' ve müzikten evliliğine kadar bilinmeyenleri anlattı. betül 07 Kasım 2017 Salı 12:21 
Ünlü sanatçı Serdar Ortaç bir radyo programına katıldı. Serdar Ortaç'a mutlu bir evliliğinin olduğunu ve bunu şöhretine ve bunca göze rağmen nasıl başardığı soruldu, Ortaç evlendiği sırada mutlu bir evlilik için Orhan Gencebay'ın kendisine verdiği bir öğüdü uyguladığını söyledi. 
Ortaç, "Orhan Gencebay bana 5-6 sene önce, ben evlenmeden önce şunu söylemişti: "Evleniyorsun bak, eğer mutlu bir yuvada devam etmek istiyorsan şunlara dikkat etmelisin: Birincisi, dip dibe yaşamayacaksın hem senin hem eşinin özel hayatları olacak, karışmayacaksın. İkincisi, üç tane kelimeyi ezberleyeceksin; 'Haklısın', 'olabilir', 'evet aşkım'. Bu üç kelimeyi ezberlersen hanımın da mutlu olur hayatınızda. Ben İrlanda'ya eşimi ailesinden istemeye gittim. 
Eşimin babası bir tek şartla evet dedi; "Happy Wife, Happy Life". Eğer bunu yapabileceksen 'tamam' dedi. Mutlu olmak ve depresyona girmemek için her şeye evet. Eşime, arkadaşıma, dostuma, anneme, kardeşime de öyleyim, rahmetli babama da öyleydim. 
Üç gün sonra doğru bir zaman ve doğru bir yerde bir kahve içerken, "Aşkım sen instagrama şu mini etekli resmini yükledin, bana yükleyeyim mi diye sordun, ben de 'evet' dedim. Hatırlıyor musun? Bence yüklememeliydin! Bak, kötü yorumları da aldın görüyor musun?" deyince zaten ders alıyor karşı taraf" diyerek mutlu bir evliliğin üç önemli formülünü anlattı. 
"SAĞLIĞIMDA DIŞARDAN İYİYİM AMA İÇERİDEN YANIYORUM" 
Serdar Ortaç , sağlığı ile ilgili dışarıdan iyi gözükmesine rağmen aslında hastalığından dolayı çok acı çektiğini söyleyerek, "Dıştan iyiyim; ama içeriden yanıyorum. 
Sanki çimentoyu, alçıyı belime dökmüşler gibi. Sahnede 'Yaz Yağmuru'nu okuyorum mesela, hop, yana kayıyorum toparlıyorum kendimi devam ediyorum. Bu konserleri yapmazsan evde oturup kendimi yerim. O yüzden hiç önemli değil, atlatacağım bu hastalığı da" dedi. 
"OSMANLILAR GEÇMİŞTE İRLANDA'YI YOK OLMAKTAN KURTARDI" 
İrlandalıların Türklerle yakın bir diyaloğu olduğunu söyleyen ünlü şarkıcı, "550 sene önce Osmanlı'nın büyük olduğu dönemde, İrlanda açlık krizine giriyor. 
Yollarda, fareler gezinir hale geliyor ve binlerce İrlandalı ölüyor. Tarihin derin sayfaları bunlar. Bir tek Osmanlı İmparatorluğu, üç tane koca gemiyle, aç kalmasınlar diye kutu kutu patatesleri yüklüyor gönderiyor. 
Bizim tarlalarımızdan çıkan bütün patatesleri İrlanda'ya gönderiyor. Osmanlı dışında dünyada kimse İrlanda'ya yardım etmiyor. Ondan sonra İrlandalılar, 'Türkler bizi kurtardı' diye yazmıştır tarih kitaplarına. İrlandalıların mutfağında yemeklerin yüzde doksanı patatestir. Bu gelenekleri oradan kalma. Irkları tükeniyorken, Osmanlı gidiyor, yardım ediyor onlara. Dibinde İngiltere var yardım etmiyor, yanında Amerika var yardım etmiyor, üstünde İskoçya var yardım etmiyor, Osmanlı gönderiyor. İrlanda'nın Türklerle böyle bir sıcaklığı var" ifadelerini kullandı. 
"TÜRKİYE EUROVİSİON ŞARKI YARIŞMASINA KATILMALI" 
İrlanda'dan Serdar Ortaç 'a eşi ile birlikte İrlanda adına Eurovision şarkı yarışmasına katılmasına yönelik bir teklif gelirse katılmayacağını söyleyerek, "Eşime hiçbir konuda hayır demem; ama iş konusunda diyebilirim. Eurovision şarkı yarışmasına birlikte katılmamız için teklif geldi diyelim. Uğraşamam ben Eurovision'la. O da zaten benim gönlümün olmadığı hiçbir şeye ısrar etmez" şeklinde konuştu. 
Ortaç Türkiye'nin Eurovision'a katılmaması ile ilgili de şunları söyledi: "Eurovision'da bir kere birinci olduk, daha ne istiyoruz, on kere mi birinci olalım? Galatasaray'ın UEFA Şampiyonu olması gibi. Katılsak iyi olur, niye soyutluyorsun ki kendini dünyadan. Katıl, bulun. Eurovision Şarkı Yarışmasında bence bulunmak gerekir, dünyanın içinde olmak gerekir".

posts.text: مشاهير بلغة السينما والجمهور تصنف كممثلة دور ثان أو "سنيدة"، إلا أن البصمة التي تركتها في أفلام عديدة شاركت بها مثل "أفواه وأرانب" جعلت منها بطلة في عيون الكثير من النقّاد، فبغض النظر عن سنوات النشاط الفني التي تزيد على 60 عامًا، إلا أن موهبتها الفطرية التي أثقلتها بدراسة التمثيل جعلت منها فنانة "مثقفة" تدرك أبعاد الشخصيات التي تلعبها، بما لا يستدعي إعادة تصوير مشاهدها أكثر من مرة، كما يحدث مع الكثير من الفنانين، وهو ما أوضحته هي في أحد لقاءاتها التليفزيونية. ويرصد "التحرير - لايف" 16 معلومة عن الفنانة القديرة رجاء حسين في التقرير التالي: 1- ولدت رجاء حسين إسماعيل في يوم 7 نوفمبر من عام 1937، بكفر طحا في محافظة القليوبية، لأب يعمل موظفًا في الحكومة، وأم ربة منزل لم تتعلم، ولها 5 إخوة (3 بنات وولدان) هي أكبرهم. 2- انتقلت مع أسرتها للعيش في طنطا بحكم وظيفة والدها، ودخلت مدرسة "الست مباركة" الابتدائية، واستمرت حتى وصلت لمرحلة التعليم الثانوي في مدرسة "طنطا". 3- علاقتها بالتمثيل بدأت من خلال مشاهدتها لزميلاتها في مسرح مدرسة "طنطا"، وظلت تراقبهم كل يوم في البروفة، إلى أن فازت بدور في المسرحية في إصابة ممثلة أخرى، وفق ما ذكرته في حوار تليفزيوني مع برنامج "استوديو وان" على قناة "نايل لايف". 4- رفض والدها اقتحامها مجال التمثيل لكنها أصرت، واستغلت فرصة سفره للعمل بالفيوم، واصطحبت والدتها وإخوتها الخمسة للقاهرة وتحديدًا حي شبرا لتحقيق حلمها. 5- التحقت بكلية الحقوق، ثم توفي والدها وبعد فترة قصيرة لحقت به والدتها، ثم إحدى شقيقاتها، فتفرغت لمجال التمثيل من أجل الإنفاق على تربية باقي إخوتها. 6- درست التمثيل في المعهد العالي للفنون المسرحية، وانضمت إلى فرقة نجيب الريحاني في عام 1957، بعد أن تم الاستعانة بها بشكل طارئ عوضًا عن الممثلة زوزو شكيب لتجسيد دور معين، ثم تعاقدت معها الفرقة مقابل 10 قروش عن البروفة و20 قرشًا عن العرض الواحد، وكانت تنفق 10 منها في شراء روايات نجيب محفوظ من سور الأزبكية. 7- عُينت في المسرح القومي وهي بعمر السابعة عشرة بعد اجتياز الاختبارات براتب 15 جنيهًا، ولكن الصحافة حينها هاجمت إدارة المسرح لتعيينها وجها غير معروف، خاصة وأنها كانت لا تزال طالبة، وظلت تعمل به حتى هذا الوقت؛ لأنها تعشق المسرح وتعتبره بيتها الثاني. 8- كانت من أوائل الفنانات اللاتي شاركن في دراما التليفزيون المصري مع مطلع الستينيات، وعن ذلك قالت: "أنا كنت بامثل في التليفزيون وهو طوب أحمر وكنا بنسجل حلقة كاملة بدون توقف لأن ماكانش فيه مونتاج وقتها". 9- أول ظهور سينمائي لها كان في فيلم "قلوب الناس" مع فاتن حمامة وأنور وجدي في عام 1954، ثم شاركت بدور صغير في فيلم "الخرساء" مع سميرة أحمد، لتبدأ بعد ذلك مسيرة النجومية الحقيقية في عالم السينما مع المخرج يوسف شاهين من خلال فيلم "العصفور". 10- قالت عن المخرج يوسف شاهين إنه "أناني وعايز الممثل ليه هو وبس.. وفي اتنين هما اللي فلتوا منه محمود المليجي وأنا"، وذلك خلال حوارها مع الفنان سمير صبري في برنامج "ماسبيرو". 11- يعتبر دور "جمالات" في فيلم "أفواه وأرانب" من أهم الأدوار التي جسدتها مع الفنانة فاتن حمامة، مصرحة في برنامج "قصر الكلام" بأنها حصلت على الجائزة الأولى عن الفيلم، لكنها سُحبت منها وتم منحها لسيدة الشاشة العربية فاتن حمامة، لتحصل هي على الجائزة الأولى عن الدور الثاني. 12- شاركت في عدد كبير من المسلسلات أهمها "الشهد والدموع|، أحلام الفتى الطائر، المال والبنون، ذئاب الجبل وريا وسكينة". 13- تقضي معظم يومها بالمسرح القومي لحضور "البروفة" صباحًا، ثم العودة إليه مساءً لتقديم العرض الحي، ومن أشهر مسرحياتها "بداية ونهاية" و"عازب و3 عوانس". 14- تزوجت في السبيعينيات من الفنان سيف عبد الرحمن الذي أعجب بها بعد حضوره مسرحية "الناس اللي فوق"، فنشأت بينهما قصة حب سرعان ما تحولت لزواج استمر ما يزيد على 50 عامًا، وأنجبت منه "كريم وإيمان". 15- اعترفت في لقاء سابق بأن زوجها خانها عدة مرات، لكنها صبرت عليه وتحملت في سبيل استمرار الأسرة، ولكنها لم تواجهه بهذا الأمر من قبل. 16- تلقت في 2014 أقسى الصدمات في حياتها بعد وفاة نجلها العقيد أركان حرب "كريم" عن عمر 42 عامًا، وعن ظروف الوفاة قالت خلال لقائها في برنامج "معكم": "خلص شغله ونزل ركب عربيته علشان يجيلي، لكنه تعب في الطريق وشافه اتنين ركبوا معاه العربية ونقلوه للمستشفى، وبمجرد دخوله كان مات بهبوط في الدورة الدموية"، أما عن تلقيها الخبر فقالت: "ماكانش حد يجرؤ يبلغني الخبر، لذلك اتصلت بيا بنتي وقالتلي بابا تعبان في المستشفى، ولما رحت معاها لقيت ضباط كتير واقفين وواحد بيقولي البقاء لله، قولته سيف مات؟ قال لا ابنك كريم تعيشي إنت"، وتابعت وهي تبكي: "أنا لقيت نفسي عمالة أضحك بشكل غير طبيعي وماشوفتش بعدها الدنيا شكلها إزاي". رجاء حسين

posts.text: false Publicidad: Un estudio del laboratorio de Fisiopatología Vascular de Parapléjicos, premiado por la Sociedad Española de Cardiología Martes, 07 de noviembre de 2017 Imprimir El laboratorio de Fisiopatología Vascular del Hospital Nacional de Parapléjicos , centro dependiente del Servicio de Salud de Castilla-la Mancha , ha sido galardonado con uno de los cinco premios en la categoría de Proyectos de Investigación Básica de la Sociedad Española de Cardiología. Según ha informado en nota de prensa el Gobierno regional, bajo el título ‘Variaciones del perfil molecular por la edad y la estratificación del riesgo cardiovascular’, el estudio persigue la identificación de una huella molecular específicamente asociada a un elevado riesgo cardiovascular en la población joven, de tal manera que pueda mejorar eficazmente las herramientas actuales existentes de predicción de enfermedad a medio y largo plazo. “La complejidad del estudio hace necesaria la aplicación de nuevas estrategias experimentales, como la proteómica, ciencia que estudia a gran escala la estructura y función de las proteínas, para obtener nuevos datos que aporten luz a las enfermedades cardiovasculares”, ha explicado la investigadora responsable del laboratorio de Fisiopatología Vascular del Hospital de Parapléjicos , María Eugenia González Barderas . “El abordaje directo sobre las muestras de plasma de sujetos con más o menos predisposición a tener una enfermedad cardiovascular, permitirán conocer de forma no invasiva su mapa proteico”, ha añadido. El estudio lo lleva a cabo un equipo multidisciplinar compuesto por María Eugenia González Barderas, Luís Rodríguez Padial, Tatiana Martín Rojas , Montserrat Baldán Martín , José Moreu , Finn Akerstrom y Nerea Corbacho Alonso , todos ellos investigadores básicos y clínicos de Castilla-La Mancha. PROYECTO PROTEOMA HUMANO El estudio premiado por la Sociedad Española de Cardiología se enmarca dentro de la iniciativa internacional ‘Human Proteome Project’, en el que la científica del Hospital de Parapléjicos, María Eugenia González Barderas y el cardiólogo del Hospital Virgen de la Salud de Toledo , Luís Rodríguez Padial, junto con el Instituto de Investigación Sanitaria de la Fundación Jiménez Díaz de Madrid , dirigido por Fernando Vivanco , forman el ‘Nodo Madrid-Toledo’ de investigación. El ‘Human Proteome Project’ es un ambicioso estudio cuyo principal objetivo consiste en la identificación y cuantificación de todas las proteínas codificadas por los más de 20.000 genes que componen el genoma humano, tanto en tejidos normales como en patológicos. La ‘Human Proteome Organization’ (HUPO) es un consorcio internacional formado por multitud de laboratorios distribuidos por todo el mundo, que ha desarrollado iniciativas de gran calado científico conocidas en este ámbito como HUPO-Liver, HUPO-Plasma, HUPO-Kidney-Urine, Brain, Cardiovascular y Stem cells. Además del Hospital Nacional de Parapléjicos, la participación española incluye otros 13 laboratorios, distribuidos por toda la geografía nacional y que pertenecen al CSIC, a diversas universidades, hospitales (Institutos de Investigación Sanitaria acreditados) y centros de investigación. posts.text:
本帖最后由 杨羊羊 于 2017-11-7 16:58 编辑
支持活动。。。。 冬天天气干燥，不仅仅是肌肤，连头发都感受到干干的。
寒风一吹，就会出现凌乱、发尾打结的问题呢。
整个头发都是乱乱的。
想要秀发变得柔软有光泽，平滑坚韧，就得好好地护肤。
冬天对付秀发干燥的小秘诀就是使用温和的洗护产品。
平时多用修护头发的洗发水，滋养头发。
而我更是在洗头后，一定要使用护发素来巩固头发的呵护呢。
我使用的是超级好用好闻的淳萃椰香沁润护发素！
美洲热销（ NO.2 in USA NO.3 in Canada ）系列，利用椰香沁润清爽的无硅**，清爽椰汁和香草成分让秀发柔顺、闪亮并丰富矿物成分保湿、滋润秀发。
全球搜索热度 Top 1 的明星成分“椰汁”富含多种矿物微量元素，深度为秀发解渴；“香草”可柔和滋润，秀发散发丝质光泽，即刻补水，水漾闪亮。
平时我都特爱喝椰子汁的。
打开绿色的盖子，挤出护发素。
乳白色的护发素，特别的稠。
超级好浓郁的椰子香味，真的特别特别的清甜。
感觉就像把椰子汁倒在头发上，散发的香气，特别的愉悦身心呢。
柔滑的护发素轻轻地摸在洗头抹半干的头发与发梢上，
头发变得特别的光滑，香气弥漫着空气。
轻揉着几分钟，待护发素的精华深入头发中，修复受损的头发。
并为头发带来着营养与滋润。
椰汁：富含多种矿物微量元素，深度为秀发解渴
香草：柔和滋润，秀发散发丝质光泽
再用清水清洗，很简单的一步，并不难清洗。
头发变得特别的顺滑，用梳子梳头发，不再打结呢。
使用后的头发，干透后，变得有光泽。
我尤其喜欢的是，那一阵从发丝散发出来的椰子香保持着一整天。
真的好好闻啊。好喜欢！
如果醒来干发的时候，头发特别的毛燥。
还可以使用淳萃 5 重植萃水润净油精华水 来修护头发，让头发一整天都特别的柔顺！
富含五种植物功效：芦荟的水润功能；茶树油的净化功能；柠檬草的清新功能；橙花的活力功能；薄荷的舒缓功能，组合出击给秀发五重呵护。
这个很清新的瓶装，绿色的透出精华水，感觉来自大自然的精华。
含有多种植物精华元素，让头发得到很好的呵护。
茶树油是萃取自绿茶的天然成分，它可以刺激微循环，促进水分和油脂的平衡，令洗后秀发倍感清爽。
原产于热带，具有抗菌镇静能力，对于发根和发梢都有良好的舒缓效果。
这个精华水的有开锁的开关，按一下就是开，再按一下就是关。
这样的设计很精妙，让瓶装设计贴合我们的生活，让我们使用起来更方便呢。
这个精华水具有芦荟精华。
富含多种维生素和矿物质，具有补水保湿的功效；还可促进头发微循环，强壮发根。芦荟在清洁头皮的同时仍可保持清透水润，令发丝不干涩、易打理，令发丝自然飘逸。
具有淡淡的清香，非常的好闻。
橙花精油是从橙花中提取，并因其自然明媚的香氛和舒缓镇静的净化与舒缓功效，可以使发根至发梢摆脱干枯和油腻的困扰，令秀发柔软飘逸。
使用前的头发，很乱哦。
喷上一些精华水，薄荷富含薄荷醇和薄荷酮等元素，气味清新，深入净化头皮，使头皮更好地呼吸。舒缓头皮发痒、清除多余油脂的同时，还可以强健脆弱的发根。
使用后，头发变得特别的清爽光滑。
梳起来，很容易，让我的头发变得有光泽不打结呢。
还可有效平衡油脂分泌，调理油性发质。

posts.title: El encuentro de Isleros y Costeros fue todo un éxito
posts.text:
Este Sábado y Domingo se celebró el Encuentro de Isleros y Costeros en el Rancho Cultural de Bajada de La Cruz.
Participaron del encuentro más de 500 personas cada día, entre ellas familias de la zona y público en general que se acercaron a disfrutar de las actividades que se desarrollaron esos dos días. 
Familias de la ribera elaboraron comidas que se compartieron con todos los que concurrieron al Rancho.
En el mismo evento se vendieron artesanías elaborados en el marco del taller "La Paz Crea" de elementos autóctonos. 
También se llevó a cabo una competencia en canoas que consistía en realizar el recorrido de ida y vuelta a la isla, entregándose premios a las distintas categorías que participaron. 
Participaron distintos músicos locales como Pituco Martínez, Mange Casis, Los Hermanos López, Aires de mi Tierra, entre otros. Desde el Gobierno de la Ciudad de La Paz se declaró el “Encuentro de Isleros y Costeros” de Interés Cultural.

Cumhurbaşkanı Recep Tayyip Erdoğan , İstanbul Haliç Kongre Merkezi 'nde "Yeni AKM Projesi"nin tanıtım programında konuştu. " Türkiye 10 yıl önce yapması gereken bir işe ancak bugün başlayabiliyor" diyen Erdoğan özetle şunları söyledi: 
2019'UN İLK ÇEYREĞİNDE BİTECEK: "Bakanlığımızdan, belediyemize ve mimarlarımıza kadar bu projenin ortaya çıkmasında emeği geçen herkesi şahsım ve milletim adına tebrik ediyorum. İnşallah az önce de değerli mimarımızın da ifade ettiği gibi 2019'un ilk çeyreğinde tamamlanıp hizmete girdiğinde Atatürk Kültür Merkezi , İstanbulumuz için gerçekten yüz akı, sembol bir mekân haline gelecektir. Açılışının üzerinden bir yıl geçtikten sonra yangın felaketi sebebiyle kapılarını kapatmak zorunda kalmıştır. 1977'nin ardından depreme dayanıksız olduğunun ortaya çıkmasına kadar verdiği hizmetler önemlidir. İncelemeler, bu binanın artık kullanılamayacağını göstermiştir. 
O YILLARIN HESABINI KİM VERECEK: 10 yıl önce başlaması gereken bir işe bugün başlanıyor. AKM'yi çoktan milletin hizmetine sunmuş olmalıydık. Ülkemizin kaybettiği yılların hesabını kim verecek? İstanbul'da inşa etiğimiz yeni havalimanı ve diğer büyük projeleri engellemek için uğraşan güç ile Suriye ve Irak'taki operasyonlarımızı sabote etmeye çalışan el aynıdır. 
SIRADA ANKARA VAR SABOTE EDENLER DE KULLANACAK: Biz proje tanıtım töreninde birarada bulunduğumuz AKM'nin yeniden inşası konusunda da sabırlı bir duruş sergiledik. Hedeflerimizden de taviz vermeden işte bugüne geldik. Daha işlevsel bir şekilde inşa edilecek yeni Atatürk Kültür Merkezi'nden en çok sabote etmek için uğraşanların yararlanacağını da biliyorum. Onların yanlış yolda gidiyor olmaları bizi doğru işler yapmakta alıkoyamadı. Zaten mermerlerine varıncaya kadar her şeyleri sundular. Beraberce bakanımla birlikte şu uygundur, şu değildir hazırlıklarını yaptık. Adım adım takip edeceğiz. İşimize sahip çıkmazsak bunun sonucunu yakalamak da mümkün değildir. MUASIR MEDENİYET: Yeni bazı adımlar Ankaramız'da da atacağız. Bunlar aynı zamanda örnek hale gelecektir. Proje üretemeyenlerin milleti hedef alan tavırları ise içinde bulundukları çaresizliğin ifadesi. Çalışsalar, terleseler, dirsek çürütseler bütün sorunlar çözülecek. Türkiye taklit seviyesinin bile gerisinde bir kültür üretimine mahkûm edilmiştir. Bugün biz de muasır medeniyetler seviyesinin üzerine çıkma hedefini isabetli buluyor ve ona sahip çıkıyoruz." West Papuan refugees in PNG urged to register 8:26 pm on 7 November 2017 Share this Share on Facebook 
West Papuan refugees in Papua New Guinea are being urged by the country's authorities to register for citizenship. 
This week PNG's Immigation and Citizenship Service Authority appealed to all West Papuans living in the Niugini islands region to get in contact. Rainbow settlement in Port moresby, Papua New Guinea, where West Papuan refugees have squatted for years. Photo: RNZI / Johnny Blades 
It's the latest stage in a project to register and formalise the status of all West Papuan refugees in PNG which has been underway almost three years. 
There are an estimated 10,000 of the refugees living in PNG, most of whom fled from neighbouring Indonesia in a mass exodus in 1984. 
Many of the refugees live in remote parts of PNG such as Western Province, the porous province abutting PNG's border with Indonesia's Papua region 
As part of its project to update its database and register the refugees, the Authority has already covered Southern and Momase regions. 
To date, over a thousand West Papuans have been granted PNG citizenship. 
The authority is now trying to register as many West Papuans as possible in the Islands region, which includes Manus province where a number of the refugees have lived for four decades or more. 
According to a spokesperson from the Authority, once refugees make contact for registration, they can then obtain citizenship. 
Before 2014, the fee for West Papuans seeking PNG citizenship was 10,000 kina, but the government has since made it free for this group of people. 
Citizenship status allows the refugees to have full rights and access to public swervices as other Papua New Guineans. Tags:

posts.title: 100张罚单276万罚金冠绝中超史 U23外援新政催新气象_中超_新浪竞技风暴_新浪网
posts.text:
罚单破百 从“秦升踩”到“稀哲扇” 邢成博 足球城
半岛全媒体记者 邢成博
震惊四座的世林赞，王小平开出的一张张罚单，U23新政下的各队万象，洋枪们攻击力的整体下滑……刚刚过去的周末，2017赛季落下了帷幕。本赛季是中国足协实施新政的首个赛季，联赛冠军依然归属了广州恒大，三线和恒大争冠的上港联赛屈居亚军，亚冠无缘决赛，足协杯挺进决赛，恒大在中超的统治力已经受到了前所未有的挑战。而诸如华夏幸福、天津权健这两支联赛新贵通过一个赛季的出色发挥最终居联赛的三、四名。回首这个闹剧频出的赛季，U23新政和外援新政的推出给联赛带来了很多新特色。这个争议巨多的赛季到底给我们留下了什么深刻的记忆呢？
罚单破百 从“秦升踩”到“稀哲扇”
本赛季，中国足协加强了2017赛季裁判员的执法尺度，重压之下并没有彻底压制住中超赛场的各项犯规，但是罚单数目和金额却直线攀升。2016赛季中超一共只有61张罚单，到了2017赛季罚单数量来到100多张，罚款总金额高达276万元！涉及球员、教练、俱乐部官员的禁赛多达247场，16家俱乐部有15家受到处罚，只有河北华夏幸福俱乐部没有被处罚过，这都创下了中超的历史纪录！
其中几张罚单触目惊心到可以写入中超历史，中超第二轮申花对阵权健，秦升在比赛中在一次无球情况下踩踏比利时国脚维特塞尔，被直接红牌罚下。事后足协对秦升的处罚异常严厉，除了罚款12万外，秦升被足协禁赛半年。从3月12号到9月11号，秦大将军守了六个月的饮水机。赛季中段上港的奥斯卡在对阵富力的比赛中，死球状态下闷人，被足协以非道德侵犯他人的名义，处以8场中超禁赛并罚款4万元人民币。奥斯卡的罚单也开启了上港全民挨罚的序幕，主帅博阿斯和多名官员多次出言不慎遭到足协处罚；武磊和浩克更是因为穿有带讽刺足协意味的T恤谢场，遭到足协停赛2场的处罚；艾哈迈多夫采访时抨击裁判被足协禁赛两场。赛季末国安和力帆的比赛中张稀哲掌掴陈雷，被禁赛12场罚款6万元，再加上不握手、骂裁判、赛场冲突和孙世林点赞等处罚，造就了一个罚单空前的赛季。
U23新政 从走过场到成效可观
年初，中国足协一纸通知催生了一个新名词：U23新政。规定每场比赛每支球队至少要有一名23岁以下的球员首发出场，而且还要有至少一名23岁以下的球员进入18人大名单。从联赛开始，很多球队就耍起了心机，不少球队的U23球员都只是走个过场，20分钟以内就会被换下。不过随着时间推移，各队逐渐接受新政，赛季末新政更是迎来大爆发。翻看U23球员出场时间榜，河南建业以7221分钟排名第一，天津权健5681分钟紧随其后，也就是说建业平均每场比赛年轻球员都能保证以首发主力方式出战。龙成、胡靖航、钟晋宝三人均进入到了U23出场名单的前10行列，甚至在某些中超场次中，还有三人同时登场的情况出现。权健的刘奕鸣、郑达伦、张修维等小将均在比赛中表现出了与年龄不符的实力和状态。让主帅能大胆使用，根本不必为新政担忧。而排名倒数第一的延边富德整个赛季U23球员上场679分钟，也就是说平均下来U23球员出场时间不超过20分钟。U23球员在这些球队中只能镇守球队在场上最薄弱的一环，主帅不敢冒险给他们太多的登场时间。
一个赛季下来，新政还是发掘了一些本土年轻球员，高准翼、黄政宇、刘奕鸣三名U23年龄段的主力中后卫随着中超出场时间的累积不断丰富经验，韦世豪、郑达伦、巴顿等球员也在进攻端展现出一定的创造力。
射手分化 压缩洋枪土炮发威
2017赛季中超外援也发生了重大变化，从之前的“3+1”变为三外援政策，每场比赛每支球队累计只能出场三名外援，不单独区分亚洲外援。这让原本各队的中后卫、后腰、前腰、中锋这条中轴线的四外援配置，改为必须至少放弃一个位置的外援使用。不少球队选择牺牲前腰位置，这对于前锋提出了更高要求，不仅要破门还要组织中前场进攻。在更加严苛的条件限制下，一些外援表现得依然相当出色，比如上港的浩克，贡献了17个进球和12次助攻的全面数据。富力前锋扎哈维打进27球，成为本赛季中超联赛最佳射手。华夏幸福能有机会拿到亚冠名额也正是拜打进20粒进球送出15个助攻的拉维奇所赐。不过受制于政策，大牌外援如埃神一般也只能坐上冷板凳。
值得欣喜的是，三外援的政策给了国内球员更多的发挥空间，缩减了外援进球比例之后，本土球员开始崛起，其中武磊在中超联赛中创纪录地打入20球，排名联赛第二。值得一提的是，在中超历史上，单赛季能打进20粒以上联赛进球的本土射手包括武磊在内一共只有3人，前两者分别是2006年的李金羽和郑智，从2006年至今11年来武磊是中超第一人。
格局大变 恒大霸业受到空前挑战
从恒大冲超的处子赛季就以升班马身份问鼎冠军，到今年的七连冠，恒大近年来刷爆了纪录。可是如果放在去年，恒大还可以笑傲群雄独孤求败，事到如今第八冠路在何方还真不好说。
前六个夺冠的赛季，恒大每年都有代表作，两次亚冠冠军，两次打破单赛季中超得分纪录，两次创造队史最长连胜。此前国安、鲁能和申花轮番追赶，都未能威胁到恒大的冠军地位。上赛季江苏苏宁奋力追赶，也不过在联赛、足协杯和超级杯拿了三个亚军。但是这个赛季，恒大险些翻船。本赛季后半段保利尼奥离队，黄博文重伤赛季报销，郑智也受到伤病困扰连续无法出场，导致恒大在中后场缺兵少将，对攻防两端影响极大。而上港疯狂烧钱之后坐拥浩克和奥斯卡两大王牌，完全具备和恒大掰手腕的实力。在足协杯的赛场，恒大两次遭遇上港全部落败。在亚冠赛场，恒大面对上港首回合失利的情况下次回合奋力追分却还是被点球淘汰。两个赛场被上港终结之后，如果不是上港奥斯卡和傅欢两大主力遭遇长时间停赛，加上多线作战球队阵容厚度相对不足，可能在联赛层面七连冠也不会到来了。除上港之外，升班马天津权健中超首赛季拿到亚冠资格，河北华夏异军突起，这都对外援阵容和本土球员年龄不再是中超第一的恒大造成了威胁。

posts.text:
Masood Azhar's nephew killed in Pulwama encounter: Army will neutralise any terrorists on Indian soil, says Bipin Rawat India IANS Nov, 07 2017 14:58:25 IST 
New Delhi: Army Chief General Bipin Rawat on Tuesday said the army would neutralise any terrorists entering Indian territory, after Indian forces killed the nephew of Jaish-e-Muhammad chief Masood Azhar in Pulwama in a gunfight. File image of Army Chief General Bipin Rawat. News18 
The Army chief also said the recovery of an assault rifle used by NATO forces in Afghanistan with the killed Jaish terrorists showed that they were getting support from the other side of the border, in a reference to Pakistan. 
Talha Rasheed, nephew of Masood Azhar, was among three militants killed in a gunfight with forces in Aglar village in Pulwama in south Kashmir on Monday night. 
"Operations are going on. As I said, the operations will continue. If any terrorists carry out activities that put the life and property of our citizens at risk, if they target any building, police station or army, they are troubling the citizens. Our attempt would be to neutralise whoever is involved in terror activities," General Rawat said on the sidelines of an event in Delhi. 
"Whether it is the nephew of Maulana Masood or anyone else, we are concerned only with finishing terror. We are not concerned what is their religion or other things," he said. 
Along with Rasheed, two more terrorists — Mehmood Bhai, a foreign terrorist, and Wasim Ahmed Ganai, a local terrorist were killed. 
Among the items recovered from the terrorists, were M4 carbines, a shorter and lighter variant of the American origin M-16 A2 assault rifle. The seizure comes days after a picture of a Hizbul Mujahideen terrorist was circulated on social media holding another variant of the M-16 rifle. 
The American origin gun is used by NATO forces in Afghanistan, and questions have been raised how it reached the terrorists. 
Asked about the presence of the weapon with the terrorists, General Rawat said, "You can see sometime back this weapon was shown in media that they (terrorists) have this weapon. It shows they are getting support across the border." 
The forces also recovered AK-74 rifles, pistols, and matrix sheets from the terrorists. 
One army soldier was also killed in the firefight.

posts.text: اسمه على قوائم اعتقال النظام السوري.. 8 معلومات عن مكسيم خليل مكسيم خليل مشاهير ظلت شهرته في إطارها المحلي بالدراما السورية، حيث شارك في عدد من الأدوار بها منذ عام 1998، لكن بداية علاقته بالجمهور المصري كانت من خلال تجسيد دور محام متلاعب في مسلسل (الشك) مع كوكبة من نجوم الفن على رأسهم حسين فهمي ومي عز الدين، ومن هنا بدأ نجمه يلمع أكثر في سماء الفن على مستوى الوطن العربي. ويرصد لكم (التحرير - لايف) 8 معلومات عن الفنان السوري مكسيم خليل بالتقرير التالي. 1- اسمه الكامل مكسيم هاني خليل، وهو من مواليد 7 نوفمبر عام 1978، في مدينة حمص بدولة سوريا. 2- ورث جينات الفن عن والده (هاني خليل) ووالدته (ستيلا خليل) فنانة المكياج والتجميل. 3- بدأ مشواره الفني في عام 1998 من خلال مجموعة أدوار بالدراما السورية، كان أولها دوره في مسلسل (أسعد الوراق)، ثم مسلسل (المسلوب) ومن بعده (البحث عن صلاح الدين)، ليكتسب شهرة لدى الجمهور السوري، ويشارك في عدد كبير من الأعمال الدرامية أبرزها (انتقام الوردة) و(أحلام كبيرة) و(الظاهر بيبرس) و(قتل الربيع). 4- خاض أول تجربة في الأداء الصوتي من خلال دبلجة شخصية (مهند) في مسلسل (نور)، وكان سببًا في شهرته على مستوى الوطن العربي. 5- حصل في عام 2009 على جائزة (أدونيا) كأفضل ممثل دور ثان عن مسلسل "زمن العار"، كما نال جائزة (الموركس) عام 2011، كأفضل ممثل عربي عن دوره في مسلسل (روبي). 6- شارك في مسلسل (الشك) عام 2013، وحقق ظهوره اللافت والجذاب ردود فعل إيجابية، ترتب عليه مشاركته في العام التالي بمسلسل (حلاوة الروح) مع الفنان الراحل خالد صالح. 7- يعتبر من أشد المؤيدين للثورة السورية، لذا اضطر لمغادرة سوريا بسبب تعرضه للمضايقات الأمنية، وتلقيه تهديدات مباشرة بالقتل، ورغم ذلك لا ينفي وجود مخطط خارجي لتقسيم بلاده، وذلك وفق ما صرح به في حوار تليفزيوني مع الإعلامية وفاء الكيلاني. 8- في أكتوبر 2015 أصدرت السلطات السورية مذكرتي اعتقال بحقه، الأولى صادرة من المخابرات العامة برقم 78442، والثانية من (الأمن السياسي)، وكذلك بحق زوجته (سوسن أرشيد)، وذلك بسبب آرائه المناهضة للثورة السورية، ورد على ذلك قائلًا: "وجود اسمي واسم زوجتي على قوائم المطلوبين لأفرع النظام الأمنية، وسام شرف أضعه على صدري"، وفق ما نشرته صحيفة (القدس العربي). مكسيم خليل

posts.title: Mỹ - Nhật đối phó Triều Tiên
posts.text: Mỹ - Nhật đối phó Triều Tiên Quote: Lầu Năm Góc cho rằng Bình Nhưỡng có thể sử dụng vũ khí sinh hóa học trong xung đột với Washington Ngay khi đến Nhật Bản hôm 5-11, chặng dừng chân đầu tiên trong chuyến công du 5 nước châu Á, Tổng thống Mỹ Donald Trump đã có những lời lẽ cứng rắn nhắm vào Triều Tiên. Tổng thống Mỹ Donald Trump và đệ nhất phu nhân Melania cùng với Thủ tướng Nhật Bản Shinzo Abe và phu nhân Akie chuẩn bị dùng bữa tối tại nhà hàng ở Tokyo - Nhật Bản hôm 5-11Ảnh: REUTERS Phát biểu trước hàng trăm quân nhân Mỹ và lực lượng phòng vệ Nhật Bản tại căn cứ không quân Yokota, ngoại ô thủ đô Tokyo, ông Donald Trump tuyên bố Mỹ và các đồng minh sẵn sàng bảo vệ tự do, cũng như cảnh báo các quốc gia khác không nên đánh giá thấp quyết tâm của Mỹ - một thông điệp mạnh mẽ được cho là gửi đến Bình Nhưỡng. Ngoài ra, Tổng thống Mỹ bảo đảm quân đội sẽ nhận được thêm nhiều trang thiết bị quốc phòng để thực hiện nhiệm vụ gìn giữ hòa bình, bảo vệ tự do. Ông khẳng định liên minh Mỹ - Nhật là khối đá đặt nền tảng cho an ninh khu vực trong suốt 60 năm qua. Báo Japan Times nhận định trong bối cảnh căng thẳng dâng cao liên quan đến các vụ thử hạt nhân và tên lửa của Bình Nhưỡng, Tổng thống Donald Trump sẽ tìm cách thiết lập mặt trận thống nhất với Nhật Bản và Hàn Quốc trong chuyến thăm ngày 7-11 - để đối phó với Triều Tiên thông qua cuộc hội đàm với lãnh đạo 2 quốc gia đồng minh này. Riêng Thủ tướng Abe lâu nay vẫn kiên trì ủng hộ lập trường cứng rắn của Tổng thống Mỹ đối với Triều Tiên - điều được ông chủ Nhà Trắng hoan nghênh trong bài phát biểu của mình khi gọi Nhật Bản là "đối tác quý báu và đồng minh quan trọng của Mỹ". Trong khi đó, Thủ tướng Abe nhận định chuyến thăm của ông Donald Trump là cơ hội để tăng cường hợp tác song phương, được xây dựng dựa trên "tình bạn và sự tin tưởng" giữa 2 nhà lãnh đạo này. Mối quan hệ gần gũi như thế đã được nêu bật bởi bữa ăn trưa và trận đấu golf hôm 5-11, diễn ra sau bài phát biểu nói trên của ông Donald Trump. Sang ngày 6-11, Tổng thống Donald Trump, cùng với đệ nhất phu nhân Melania, sẽ tiếp kiến Nhật hoàng và hoàng hậu. Tiếp đó, ông hội đàm chính thức với Thủ tướng Abe và gặp gỡ thân nhân của các công dân Nhật Bản đã bị điệp viên Triều Tiên bắt cóc trong thời gian chiến tranh lạnh. Tình hình Triều Tiên chắc chắn đứng đầu nội dung thảo luận giữa hai nhà lãnh đạo Mỹ - Nhật. Điều này được chính ông Donald Trump xác nhận với các phóng viên tháp tùng trên đường từ Hawaii đến Nhật Bản: "Chúng tôi mong giải quyết xong cuộc khủng hoảng này. Nó là vấn đề lớn của đất nước chúng tôi và thế giới". Thêm vào đó, ông hé lộ sẽ sớm đưa ra quyết định có thêm Triều Tiên vào danh sách các quốc gia bị cáo buộc tài trợ cho khủng bố hay không. "Hy vọng chúng tôi sẽ có thể thảo luận triệt để về các vấn đề quốc tế, trong đó có Triều Tiên" - Tổng thống Donald Trump bày tỏ. Nếu bước đi như thế của ông chủ Nhà Trắng diễn ra sẽ khiến tình hình bán đảo Triều Tiên thêm nóng giữa lúc Lầu Năm Góc nói đến kịch bản đưa lực lượng đặc nhiệm vào Bình Nhưỡng để định vị và kiểm soát toàn bộ địa điểm vũ khí hạt nhân của nước này. Trong lá thư gửi các nghị sĩ Mỹ do chuẩn đô đốc Michael Dumont chắp bút, Lầu Năm Góc cũng cảnh báo Triều Tiên có thể sử dụng vũ khí sinh học và hóa học trong trường hợp xung đột xảy ra - theo tiết lộ của báo The Washington hôm 5-11.

posts.text:
Твитнуть 
В рамках расследования уголовного производства по факту завладения средствами государственного предприятия Восточный горно-обогатительный комбинат о подозрении сообщено еще трем лицам. Об этом во вторник, 7 ноября, сообщает Экономическая правда со ссылкой на пресс-службу Национального антикоррупционного бюро Украины. 
О подозрении сообщено двум гражданам Австрии – генеральному директору и директору австрийской компании-посредника Steuermann, которая якобы подконтрольная экс-председателю комитета Верховной Рады Украины по вопросам Топливно-энергетического комплекса Николаю Мартыненко. 
Должностным лицам Steuermann инкриминируют совершение преступлений, предусмотренных ст. 255 о создании преступной организации, ст. 191 о присвоении, растратк имущества или завладении им путем злоупотребления служебным положением. 
Генерального директора австрийского ООО также подозревают в совершении преступления по ст. 209 о легализации (отмывании) доходов. 
Третий подозреваемый – гражданин Украины. Он является руководителем ряда компаний, которые систематически выигрывали тендеры в ГП ВостГОК, ГП НАЭК Энергоатом, ГП Объединенная горно-химическая компания, и одновременно является главой иностранных предприятий, задействованных в схеме отмывания средств. 
О подозрении в совершении преступлений ему сообщено в Латвийской Республике. 
Как сообщал Корреспондент.net , Николая Мартыненко задержали 20 апреля в рамках расследования уголовного производства по факту хищения средств ВостГОКа на сумму 17 миллионов долларов.

posts.text:
Publication date: Available online 6 November 2017
Source: Dental Materials
Author(s): Stefano Pieralli, Ralf-Joachim Kohal, Emilia Lopez Hernandez, Sam Doerken, Benedikt Christopher Spies
ObjectiveTo determine the osseointegration rate of zirconium dioxide (ZrO2) dental implants in preclinical investigations.DataData on the osseointegration rate was extracted considering the bone to implant contact (BIC), removal torque analysis (RTQ) and push-in tests. Meta analyses were conducted using multilevel multivariable mixed-effects linear regression models. The Šidák method was used in case of multiple testing.SourcesAn electronic screening of the literature (MEDLINE/Pubmed, Cochrane Library and Embase) and a supplementary manual search were performed. Animal investigations with a minimum sample size of 3 units evaluating implants made of zirconia (ZrO2) or its composites (ZrO2>50vol.%) were included.Study selectionThe search provided 4577 articles, and finally 54 investigations were included and analyzed. Fifty-two studies included implants made from zirconia, 4 zirconia composite implants and 37 titanium implants. In total, 3435 implants were installed in 954 animals.ConclusionsNo significant influence of the evaluated bulk materials on the outcomes of interest could be detected. When comparing different animal models, significant differences for the evaluated variables could be found. These results might be of interest for the design of further animal investigations.

posts.title: After Thor: Ragnarok, What Will Be Hulk's Fate With Marvel - A Solo Film?
posts.text: News Alerts After Thor: Ragnarok , What Will Be Hulk's Fate With Marvel - A Solo Film? Yes, No, Maybe? Hulk solo movie rights belong to Universal Studios and Marvel can only use the gamma-radiated giant in a guest star/team-up way. Will Marvel and Universal collaborate? Entertainment | David Betancourt, The Washington Post | Updated: November 07, 2017 14:52 IST 3 Shares Washington: So where does the I ncredible Hulk go from Ragnarok ?The success of Marvel Studios' not so jolly, green and gamma-radiated giant in Thor: Ragnarok - as well as his guest appearances in past and future Avengers films - has proven that the Hulk still has potential on the big screen.What isn't so clear is if the Hulk will continue to be the strongest guest star there is, or if he'll once again star in his own movie as he did back in the early days of Marvel Studios. ( The Incredible Hulk , starring Edward Norton, debuted in 2008. We won't bring up 2003's Hulk starring Eric Bana and directed by Ang Lee because we're trying to convince you that Hulk movies work, right? And that was way before the Marvel Cinematic Universe's existence anyway.)A quick Internet search can point you to the comments of actor Mark Ruffalo - the only actor who has played Bruce Banner/Hulk in multiple movies - who said in July that a Hulk movie will never happen because Universal doesn't want to play nice with Marvel Studios. If Marvel Studios wants to use the green giant in a movie, it must be in a guest star/team-up way; if they wanted to make a solo effort, Universal (who has the rights to a solo Hulk movie) would have to be involved.Marvel Studios has already proven they can share with others with their successful (and almost impossible to pull off) reboot of Spider-Man . During the early days of the Marvel Cinematic Universe, no one thought Spider-Man would be able to take part in an Avengers movie because the web-slinger's rights belonged to Sony. But Marvel Studios made a bold move in their efforts to collaborate, and Sony very wisely realized they were in danger of tarnishing a once indestructible superhero movie brand. Both sides made it work.You can almost understand Universal's hesitation to revisit the Hulk on film: Hulk movies aren't the shining example of how to make a good superhero movie. If there's one blip in the MCU, it's Norton's The Incredible Hulk movie (directed by Louis Leterrier), which ironically featured a villain called "the Abomination." Not even Robert Downey Jr.'s post-credit appearance was enough to help. And while the story line moved the MCU-connected movieverse along, it didn't leave anyone hungry for more Hulk.It's possible that Universal feels there are no more Hulk stories to tell, and that revisiting the character in a solo movie would produce more of the same ho-hum results. But if that's the mentality, that just means they don't have any comic-book people over there, like Marvel Studios does with head honcho Kevin Feige or Warner Bros./DC Entertainment does with Geoff Johns. It's important to have people who know, love and, most importantly, really care about these characters and can dive through a library's worth of stories to find the right thing to adapt for both a superhero-loving and general audience.If Universal did have executives like that, or a passionate director like, say, Wonder Woman 's Patty Jenkins (who didn't let a connected superhero movie universe prevent her from telling an incredibly singular heroic story), they'd realize there are a lot of potential options for a movie.A piece to the Hulk moviemaking puzzle is already there waiting in the MCU: William Hurt's Thaddeus Ross, Marvel Studios' military man, who resurfaced as secretary of state in 2016's Captain America: Civil War . And since the Planet Hulk comic-book story line has already been used in Thor: Ragnarok , why not revisit one of the next best Hulk tales out there for a movie adaptation: the Red Hulk?The Red Hulk is stronger, and his brain increases in strength as well, causing him to retain his intelligence when he "hulks out." His secret identity? Thaddeus Ross, who has always hated the green Hulk and Bruce Banner equally. As much as people love watching the Hulk go berserk on screen, how great would it be seeing him going up against the Rulk? (A horrible nickname, but great character.)The gray Hulk could work, too: He's not as strong, but the much more intelligent Hulk appeared in Marvel Comics during the 1980s.Everything is there to help the Hulk start smashing at the box office all by himself: the stories and the right actor. But if a solo-Hulk movie is truly never meant to happen again, at least we have the Revengers . . . I mean, Avengers . . . movies.©2017, The Washington Post (Except for the headline, this story has not been edited by NDTV staff and is published from a syndicated feed.) Trending

posts.title: В Витебской области дедушка с другом два года насиловали внуков и снимали порно
posts.text:
Твитнуть В Витебской области двое мужчин в возрасте более 50 лет более двух лет насиловали детей, среди которых были и трое внуков одного из них. Об этом сообщил старший оперуполномоченный по особо важным делам УВД Витебского облисполкома Денис Шкурко. 
Мужчины вступали в половую связь с внуками одного из подозреваемых каждые выходные, когда дети приезжали к нему в гости, и снимали все это на видео. Также они вступали в половую связь друг с другом на глазах у детей. Родители детей узнали о происходящем только через два года и сразу же обратились в милицию. Самому младшему из детей всего семь лет. 
В ходе расследования выяснилось, что товарищ "дедушки" совершал преступления против детей и ранее: в начале 2000-х годах он насиловал детей соседей по общежитию и внучку своей сожительницы. 
На суде свою вину педофилы признали не полностью, один из них до сих пор уверен, что это лишь "баловство", рассказал Денис Шкурко. 
В каком именно населенном пункте Витебской области совершались преступления, в милиции не разглашают.

thread.title: Tweeter-in-chief ready to confront China's 'great firewall'
thread.title_full: Tweeter-in-chief ready to confront China's 'great firewall' - StarTribune.com

posts.author: startribune.com
posts.title: Tweeter-in-chief ready to confront China's 'great firewall'
posts.text:
America's tweeter-in-chief is set to face off bit-to-bit against China's "great firewall." 
  arrival in Beijing on Wednesday will serve as a test of reach for his preferred 140-character communications tool. 
The White House is declining to comment on the president's ability to tweet in China or the precautions being taken to protect his communications in the heavily monitored state. It's about more than cybersecurity. Knowing the president's penchant for showmanship, some aides are trying to build up social media suspense before Air Force One is wheels-down in Beijing. 
Spoiler alert: The American president will get his way. Multiple officials familiar with the procedures in place but unauthorized to discuss them publicly said the president will, in fact, be able to tweet in China. 
Twitter is blocked for domestic users in China, but foreigners have had success accessing the social media service while using data roaming services that connect to their home cellular networks. 
For an American president, it's not that straightforward. Securing the president's communications — and tweets — in China requires satellites, sophisticated electronics and the work of hundreds on multiple continents. 
Trump, like his predecessor, has a secure cell phone, though he uses it more for tweeting than phone calls. He's sent at least two dozen tweets in the first four days of his trip to Asia. Developed in collaboration between the National Security Agency and Secret Service, it has some regular functionality disabled to protect from hacking. But China poses a distinct challenge: Merely turning it on there is a security risk, as China's cellular network is believed to be entirely compromised by its security services. 
Several former administration officials said they did not recall whether President Barack Obama brought his cell phone to China. The White House declined to say whether Trump would be bringing his phone on the trip, but tweets sent by him since he's departed Washington are marked as being sent from an iPhone. 
Chinese officials appeared to recognize the importance of the medium to their guest. Asked whether Trump would be able to tweet from Beijing, Chinese Vice Foreign Minister Zheng Zeguang told reporters on Friday: "We take everything into account on receiving foreign heads of state so you should have no reservations about Mr. President's ability to keep in touch with the outside." 
But officials said it would hardly be up to China, as it would be inconceivable for Trump's device to ever reach a Chinese network. 
The White House maintains an ever-updating set of policies and regulations for overseas travel. According to current and former White House staffers, officials are sometimes issued new devices specifically for foreign trips. Their phone numbers and emails are forwarded to the new devices for the duration of the overseas stint, then shifted back to their stateside devices once they return. The phones used on the trip are returned to the White House IT office for inspection. 
In the event the trip is to a high-risk cyber-espionage location, such as China, Israel or Cuba, aides are given extensive briefings on cybersecurity. Among the precautions: Aides are strongly discouraged from turning on their devices in the offending country. 
Former White House press secretary Josh Earnest recalled that security protocols changed frequently during the Obama administration, but that aides were encouraged to leave their personal devices on Air Force One. 
"While in the country, we were encouraged to bring everything with us whenever we left the room, even for short periods" such as a gym visit, Earnest said. "And, we were told never to use hotel provided Wi-Fi." 
But, Earnest added, it "seems reasonable that these safeguards are easy to put in place for Trump's phone." 
The White House Communications Agency, a 1,200-person military command, is responsible for the president's global communications needs. The primary role is to maintain communications for critical defense purposes, like emergency communications with military commanders. In every presidential motorcade, for instance, an armored SUV codenamed Road Runner provides for a connection to an array of military and Secret Service communications networks. Abroad, it also enables mundane presidential traffic, like tweets. 
On a trip, the WHCA, along with the White House situation room staff, maintains a secure communications suite at the presidential hotel for use by presidential staff. It includes both secure and unsecured phones, as well as access to the White House Wi-Fi network. It is swept routinely for spying devices and guarded 24/7. Overseas, "we'd have to be extra vigilant about confining classified — and even personal — discussions to this suite," recalled Ned Price, a former CIA analyst who worked as a spokesman for Obama's National Security Council.

Long post:
My daughter was born in Oct. 2015. Three short weeks into her life, she was seriously hurt at the hands of her father. I take her to the hospital for what I suspected to be colic (it was Sunday, pedi office was closed), only to find out my daughter had a bucket fracture and other injuries. CPS steps in, removes her dad from the picture, he's criminally charged with INJ to child. He had been to every prenatal appt, bought us a new car, helped set up the nursery. This was the worst surprise of my life. I never would have thought someone would be capable of that. Turns out he was under the influence, without my knowledge, and lost all of my trust. My daughter was hospitalized for three agonizing days, my milk supply started to dwindle as I was to be kept under supervision while the investigation was on going. I was a wreck, and still to this day do not trust my daughter in the hands of anyone but myself. Heck, I'm still a wreck two years later, but some how I have somewhat forgiven her father... forgiven isn't the right word... I just wanted to give him a second chance because I knew he wasn't a bad person. He had made a very very bad mistake however that can't be looked past.
But fast forward to this past July. I have an abusive, mentally ill, drug-abusing mother whom I was forced to live with along with my daughter after she was injured. I had spent from Nov. 2015 to June 2017 there walking on eggshells. (She's very prone to unpredictable outbursts. Don't want to be the next target.) I decided I'd had enough and was going to live with my daughters paternal grandmother (let's call her MIL) who had seen my daughter a grand total of 3 times since she was born, and had just moved to TX from GA.
Well, let me just say, I learned to appreciate my mother very quickly because this women was EVIL. She made up lies to try to split her son and I apart. She would talk badly about me with his sister and leave her phone out so I could see them making fun of me. She let her other 5 year old grandson push my daughter down without reprimanding him. She threatened to call cps several times with no justifiable reason. Her reason was "because I can, and they will tear your family apart and take your daughter." -with a smile on her face.
Within two weeks, we were out. I go back to work, and one day, randomly get a call from a CPS investigator wanting to see my daughter IMMEADITELY. I had my mom come pick up my DD (dear daughter) from my work, and take her home so the investigator could see her. He strips her down naked and takes photos to prove she's not abused. Then orders me straight to a lab for a UA because she said I'm a drug abuser as well. I'm shaken at this point, just because of the past. He goes around the house, complimenting it, and my daughters giant toy box. He then says that nothing that was reported matched, and obviously it was a family squabble. He just needed my drug test results and that would be it.
A week later he gets the pass results from my UA, duh!, keeps the case open a few more weeks, calls MIL (mother-in-law) who reported me to try and dig up as much dirt as he can, then comes out to see me and my daughter one more time before closing it. Nothing was found. I'm a great mom and and there's no doubt about that.
Here's the issue: how do I tell DF (dear fiancee) to make his mom F off? He won't because he's afraid she will call the police and he's non confrontational. She's really going to ruin our relationship. I know y'all have delt with in law hell so give me some guidance. I don't need this witch constantly trying to get my daughter taken away from me. It's breaking me apart inside and out to the point where I'm just filled with rage. Rage at her for being a dumb B, and rage at DF (dear fiancee) for not putting his foot down to his mother who is trying her best to get my daughter legally kidnapped. Please help. I'm 23 years old and already feel gray hair coming in after all of this. Any advice or insight is welcome.
